  "body": "**When I sync node, I am always encounter the followed issue:** \r\n```\r\nfatal error: runtime: out of memory\r\n\r\nruntime stack:\r\nruntime.throw(0xf6483c, 0x16)\r\n        /usr/local/go/src/runtime/panic.go:616 +0x81\r\nruntime.sysMap(0xc475d30000, 0x10000000, 0x0, 0x1b9a818)\r\n        /usr/local/go/src/runtime/mem_linux.go:216 +0x20a\r\nruntime.(*mheap).sysAlloc(0x1b80e00, 0x10000000, 0x7fd22800f4b0)\r\n        /usr/local/go/src/runtime/malloc.go:470 +0xd4\r\nruntime.(*mheap).grow(0x1b80e00, 0x8000, 0x0)\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n**When I check hard disk used：**\r\n\r\n```\r\nroot@VM-0-16-ubuntu:/home/ubuntu# df -k\r\nFilesystem     1K-blocks     Used Available Use% Mounted on\r\nudev              939292        0    939292   0% /dev\r\ntmpfs             191716    19840    171876  11% /run\r\n/dev/vda1       51474024 33399332  15768608  68% /\r\ntmpfs             958568       48    958520   1% /dev/shm\r\ntmpfs               5120        0      5120   0% /run/lock\r\ntmpfs             958568        0    958568   0% /sys/fs/cgroup\r\ntmpfs                100        0       100   0% /run/lxcfs/controllers\r\ntmpfs             191716        0    191716   0% /run/user/500\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n**My hard disk is 500G, My RAM is 2G， My cpu is double core**\r\n\r\n",
